title: Vaccination Service — Mundaring Village Pharmacy
description: Vaccination service at Mundaring Village Pharmacy. Flu vaccine, COVID vaccine, whooping cough vaccine, tetanus vaccine.
cleaned_text: Book a Vaccination Appointment Mundaring Village Pharmacy is fully accredited to dispense and administer many vaccinations on the Australian Immunisation register. Our Pharmacist take great care, delivering an important service to the Perth Hills community. No prescriptions necessary, simply call our store, or book in using our automated booking system below.
